tr><th colspan=\"2\">Inhabitants</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Clay_golem\" title=\"Clay golem\">Clay golem</a> (only inhabitant)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Teleports</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Magic_carpet\" title=\"Magic carpet\">Magic carpet</a> from <a href=\"/w/Shantay_Pass\" title=\"Shantay Pass\">Shantay Pass</a> (After <a href=\"/w/The_Golem\" title=\"The Golem\">The Golem</a>) <a href=\"/w/Necklace_of_passage\" title=\"Necklace of passage\">Necklace of passage</a> and run southeast from <a href=\"/w/Desert_eagle\" title=\"Desert eagle\">Desert eagle</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\">Music</th><td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/The_Golem_(music_track)\" title=\"The Golem (music track)\">The Golem</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Map</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"infobox-full-width-content infobox-image\"><a class=\"mw-kartographer-map mw-kartographer-container center\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 250px;background-image: url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_53_48.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_54_48.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_53_47.png), url(https://maps.runescape.wiki/osrs/versions/2022-04-27_a/tiles/rendered/0/2/0_54_47.png); background-position: -202px -39px, 54px -39px, -202px 217px, 54px 217px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-mw=\"interface\" data-style=\"0\" data-width=\"300\" data-height=\"250\" data-zoom=\"2\" data-lat=\"3095\" data-lon=\"3480\" data-mapid=\"0\" data-plane=\"0\" href=\"/w/Special:Map/0/2/-1/3480/3095\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<table class=\"relative-location\" style=\"float:right; width:200px; clear:right;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" class=\"relative-location-header\"><span class=\"relative-location-txt\">Location on <b><a href=\"/w/World_Map\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"World Map\"><span class=\"relative-location-txt\">World Map</span></a></b></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/w/Burgh_de_Rott\" title=\"Burgh de Rott\">Burgh de Rott</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&#8593;\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:25%\"><a href=\"/w/River_Elid\" title=\"River Elid\">River Elid</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:7.5%\">&#8592;\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%; align-items: center;\"><b>Uzer</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:7.5%\">&#8594;\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%\"><a href=\"/w/Eastern_Sea\" title=\"Eastern Sea\">Eastern Sea</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\">&#8595;\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/w/Unknown\" title=\"Unknown\">Unknown</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Uzer</b> was a prosperous city in the <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_Desert\" title=\"Kharidian Desert\">Kharidian Desert</a> famous for its clay golems. Today it is ruins, the city was destroyed during the <a href=\"/w/God_Wars\" title=\"God Wars\">God Wars</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Before_Thammaron\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Before Thammaron</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Battle_for_Uzer\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Battle for Uzer</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Getting_there\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Getting there</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Locations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Locations</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Ruins\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ruins</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Temple_basement\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Temple basement</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Throne_room\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Throne room</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#The_very_few_of_Uzer\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The very few of Uzer</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Music\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Music</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Before_Thammaron\">Before Thammaron</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Before Thammaron\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Before Thammaron\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Late in the <a href=\"/w/Third_Age\" title=\"Third Age\">Third Age</a> Uzer was an advanced civilisation whose inhabitants were expert magical craftsman. It was also the only city to have created and used Golems. According to carvings on the temple the citizens of Uzer worshipped <a href=\"/w/Saradomin\" title=\"Saradomin\">Saradomin</a>, <a href=\"/w/Zamorak\" title=\"Zamorak\">Zamorak</a> and <a href=\"/w/Armadyl\" title=\"Armadyl\">Armadyl</a> though they were ultimately aligned with Saradomin.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle_for_Uzer\">Battle for Uzer</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Battle for Uzer\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Battle for Uzer\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Uzer_underground.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Uzer_underground.png/300px-Uzer_underground.png?98fba\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"198\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Uzer_underground.png/450px-Uzer_underground.png?98fba 1.5x, /images/thumb/Uzer_underground.png/600px-Uzer_underground.png?98fba 2x\" data-file-width=\"1707\" data-file-height=\"1127\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Uzer_underground.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The underground portion of the ruins. Notice the various symbols of Thammaron, Armadyl, Saradomin and Zamorak.</div></div></div>\n<p>Sometime towards the end of the <a href=\"/w/God_Wars\" title=\"God Wars\">God Wars</a>, <a href=\"/w/Thammaron\" title=\"Thammaron\">Thammaron</a>, Zamorak's chief lieutenant, opened a portal from his own domain underneath the temple, bypassing the city's defences. Though the forces of Uzer drove him back, either a second attack by Thammaron or other Zamorakian forces destroyed the city. But before the city was destroyed an elite force of Golems raided Thammaron's lair, mortally wounding him. A single, heavily damaged Golem was the sole survivor of this assault. The survivors of the battle then fled to the city of <a href=\"/w/Ullek\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ullek\">Ullek</a>, before it too was destroyed by Zamorakians under the command of <a href=\"/w/Balfrug_Kreeyath\" title=\"Balfrug Kreeyath\">Balfrug Kreeyath</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Getting_there\">Getting there</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Getting there\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Getting there\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Magic carpet ride from <a href=\"/w/Shantay_Pass\" title=\"Shantay Pass\">Shantay Pass</a> (after completion of <a href=\"/w/The_Golem\" title=\"The Golem\">The Golem</a>).</li>\n<li>Use <a href=\"/w/Fairy_ring\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fairy ring\">fairy ring</a> code <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>D</b><b>L</b><b>Q</b></span>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Locations\">Locations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Locations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Locations\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ruins\">Ruins</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Ruins\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Ruins\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The ruins of various buildings and large kilns are in the vicinity of the temple. The large kilns were used to manufacture Golems, the temple and the Golem are all that remain above the desert sands. It is also where you can start <a href=\"/w/The_Golem\" title=\"The Golem\">The Golem</a> <a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">quest</a>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Temple_basement\">Temple basement</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Temple basement\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Temple basement\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Underneath the city lies the temple basement. To the east of the entrance <a href=\"/w/Black_mushroom\" title=\"Black mushroom\">black mushrooms</a> spawn, while in the north-west one can find a <a href=\"/w/Strange_implement\" title=\"Strange implement\">strange implement</a>. Statues of craftsmen adorn the halls while golem pieces litter the ground. A few ghosts lurk in the hallways. At the far end lies a portal to Thammaron's realm.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Throne_room\">Throne room</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=8&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Throne room\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Throne room\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/w/File:Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png/300px-Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png?05bc9\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"146\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png/450px-Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png?05bc9 1.5x, /images/thumb/Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png/600px-Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png?05bc9 2x\" data-file-width=\"1918\" data-file-height=\"935\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/w/File:Thammaron%27s_throne_room.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The throne of the elder demon.</div></div></div>\n<p>The realm of the demon Thammaron is red and grey while a causeway of horns breaking the ground lead to his throne. To the left of the entrance lies the remains of Thammaron. Members can use a hammer and chisel on the throne to receive gems. This room is also a focal part of the <a href=\"/w/Shadow_of_the_Storm\" title=\"Shadow of the Storm\">Shadow of the Storm</a> <a href=\"/w/Quest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Quest\">quest</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_very_few_of_Uzer\">The very few of Uzer</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=9&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: The very few of Uzer\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: The very few of Uzer\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Clay_golem\" title=\"Clay golem\">Clay golem</a> - the clay golem is ancient and dates back to the Third Age. Now he is broken and incomplete.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Father_Badden\" title=\"Father Badden\">Father Badden</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Music\">Music</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=10&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Music\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Music\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/The_Golem_(music_track)\" title=\"The Golem (music track)\">The Golem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Throne_of_the_Demon\" title=\"Throne of the Demon\">Throne of the Demon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Grip_of_the_Talon\" title=\"Grip of the Talon\">Grip of the Talon</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?section=11&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Uzer?action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/The_Golem\" title=\"The Golem\">The Golem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Thammaron\" title=\"Thammaron\">Thammaron</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Shadow_of_the_Storm\" title=\"Shadow of the Storm\">Shadow of